  Version bump (bug #352953). Remove mailwrapper support, add vim-syntax USE
  flag, install gnome-keyring script (bug #341113), and install find_alias
  script (bug #349869). Bump to EAPI 3, remove unused eutils eclass, and use
  CDEPEND for common dependencies.

